All grown up in post-apocalyptic 2018, John Connor 
(Christian Bale) must lead the resistance of humans 
against the increasingly dominating militaristic 
robots in this fourth installment of the popular 
action-packed Terminator series. But when Marcus 
Wright (Sam Worthington) appears, his existence 
confuses the mission as Connor tries to determine 
whether Wright has come from the future or the past 
-- and whether he's friend or foe.
